OL,3,CFormer Scotland captain Stuart Hogg
OL,4,Cgiven five-year non-harassment order
OL,6,FFormer Scotland rugby union captain
OL,7,FStuart Hogg has been sentenced to a
OL,8,Ffive-year non-harassment order and
OL,9,Ffined after breaching bail conditions
OL,10,Fby contacting his estranged wife.
OL,12,FHogg had his sentence for abusing
OL,13,FGillian Hogg over the course of five
OL,14,Fyears deferred until 9 January for
OL,15,Fclarification on whether a community
OL,16,Forder with remotely monitored
OL,17,Fsupervision can be imposed.
OL,19,FHe previously admitted breaching bail
OL,20,Fconditions by repeatedly contacting
OL,21,FMrs Hogg in June.
