OL,3,CFormer Scotland captain Stuart Hogg
OL,4,Cgiven five-year non-harassment order
OL,6,FProsecutor Drew Long told Jedburgh
OL,7,FSheriff Court on Thursday there had
OL,8,Fbeen contact between Hogg and his ex-
OL,9,Fpartner between 26 June and 30 this
OL,10,Fyear, and one night she received 28
OL,11,Ftexts from him.
OL,13,FHe said: "On the 29th of June it
OL,14,Fappears Mrs Hogg was on a night out.
OL,15,FAt 5.30am the following morning Mrs
OL,16,FHogg noted that she had received 28
OL,17,Ftext messages from Mr Hogg, five
OL,18,Fmissed calls and a voice call or voice
OL,19,Fnote lasting two minutes and 20
OL,20,Fseconds.
