OL,6,F"Later that day she had three further
OL,7,Fmessages from him and she responded
OL,8,Ftelling him to stop."
OL,10,FHe read out some of the messages,
OL,11,Fwhich included "Happy divorce, I will
OL,12,Fnever forgive you for that", "See you
OL,13,Fin court", and "ridiculous, who is
OL,14,Flooking after the kids?".
