OL,6,FMr Long told the court the messages
OL,7,FHogg sent later in the day were
OL,8,F"apologetic in tone".Sentencing Hogg
OL,9,Ffor breaching the bail conditions,
OL,10,FSheriff Peter Paterson handed him a
OL,11,Ffive-year non-harassment order,
OL,12,Fbarring him from approaching or
OL,13,Fcontacting Mrs Hogg.
