OL,6,FHe also fined him #600, with an
OL,7,Fadditional #40 victim surcharge.Hogg
OL,8,Fpreviously pleaded guilty to a single
OL,9,Fcharge of domestic abuse of Mrs Hogg
OL,10,Fwhen he appeared at Selkirk Sheriff
OL,11,FCourt on November 4.He admitted
OL,12,Fshouting and swearing, tracking her
OL,13,Fmovements and sending her messages
OL,14,Fwhich were alarming and distressing in
OL,15,Fnature.
