OL,4,Cgiven five-year non-harassment order
OL,6,FThe court previously heard he berated
OL,7,FMrs Hogg for "not being fun" after
OL,8,Fgoing on drinking binges with his
OL,9,Fcolleagues, and once sent her more
OL,10,Fthan 200 text messages in the space of
OL,11,Fa few hours which led her to have a
OL,12,Fpanic attack.
OL,14,FHogg now lives abroad and plays for
OL,15,FFrench club Montpellier, and the court
OL,16,Fwas previously told he is in the
OL,17,Fprocess of a divorce.
