OL,3,CFormer Scotland captain Stuart Hogg
OL,4,Cgiven five-year non-harassment order
OL,6,FAngela Gray KC, representing Hogg,
OL,7,Fsaid on Thursday he will be remaining
OL,8,Fin France until at least March next
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FShe also said Hogg accepts his
OL,12,Fbehaviour was "unacceptable", adding:
OL,13,F"He has made mistakes and he has
OL,14,Flearned from them. He has taken the
OL,15,Ftime to look inward and reflect."
OL,17,FSheriff Paterson said a report about
OL,18,FHogg placed before the court mentioned
OL,19,Fthe Caledonian Men's Programme, a
OL,20,Fbehaviour programme for men convicted
OL,21,Fof domestic abuse.
