OL,6,FHe said: "There is a difficulty with
OL,7,Fthat and that is that you are a non-
OL,8,Fresident of the UK.
OL,10,F"I cannot impose that at the moment.
OL,12,F"I'm not prepared to defer that till
OL,13,FMarch when you may be returning.
OL,15,F"So I will defer sentence until
OL,16,FJanuary 9 for clarification about
OL,17,Fwhether I can impose a community order
OL,18,Fwith supervision to be monitored
OL,19,Fremotely."
