OL,6,FThe sentencing in January will be at
OL,7,FSelkirk Sheriff Court.Mr Hogg, dressed
OL,8,Fin a tweed jacket and dark tie,
OL,9,Fattended court on Thursday accompanied
OL,10,Fby his parents Margaret and John and
OL,11,Fmade no comment as he left the
OL,12,Fbuilding before driving away.
OL,14,FThe 32-year-old had been due to stand
OL,15,Ftrial on November 4 but pleaded guilty
OL,16,Fthat day to a charge of domestic
OL,17,Fabuse, between 2019 and 2024 at
OL,18,Flocations including Hawick in the
OL,19,FScottish Borders.
