OL,6,FProsecutor Drew Long told the court
OL,7,Flast month that the couple moved to
OL,8,FExeter in 2019 with their three young
OL,9,Fchildren, all aged under three, but
OL,10,FHogg's "behaviour deteriorated" as he
OL,11,Fwent out partying.Hogg would "shout
OL,12,Fand swear and accuse Mrs Hogg of not
OL,13,Fbeing fun" for not joining in
OL,14,Fdrinking, and her family "noticed a
OL,15,Fchange in her", the court heard.
