OL,4,Cgiven five-year non-harassment order
OL,6,FIn 2022, Mrs Hogg went on a night out
OL,7,Fand was bombarded with text messages
OL,8,Ffrom her husband which "caught the
OL,9,Fattention of the people she was with",
OL,10,Fthe prosecutor said.The following
OL,11,Fyear, the couple moved to Hawick but
OL,12,FHogg used an app to track his wife and
OL,13,F"questioned her whereabouts" while she
OL,14,Fwas dropping the children off, Mr Long
OL,15,Ftold the court.
