OL,3,CFormer Scotland captain Stuart Hogg
OL,4,Cgiven five-year non-harassment order
OL,6,FIn 2023, Mrs Hogg decided to leave the
OL,7,Frugby player and sought advice from a
OL,8,Fdomestic abuse service.On February 21
OL,9,Fthis year, police were called due to
OL,10,FHogg "shouting and swearing" and he
OL,11,Fwas taken into custody and then placed
OL,12,Fon a bail order stipulating not to
OL,13,Fcontact Mrs Hogg, or to enter the
OL,14,Ffamily home.
OL,16,FHogg retired from professional rugby
OL,17,Flast year but in July this year it was
OL,18,Fannounced that he would be returning
OL,19,Fafter signing for Montpellier on a two-
OL,20,Fyear contract.
